#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:176
msgid "Peony"
msgstr "Peonía"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:177
msgid ""
"A peony is a large plant which occupies two blocks. It is mainly used in dye "
"production."
msgstr ""
"Una peonía es una planta grande que ocupa dos bloques. Se utiliza "
"principalmente en la protección del tinte."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:193
msgid "Rose Bush"
msgstr "Rosal"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:194
msgid ""
"A rose bush is a large plant which occupies two blocks. It is safe to touch "
"it. Rose bushes are mainly used in dye production."
msgstr ""
"Un rosal es una planta de gran tamaño que ocupa dos bloques de altura. Es "
"seguro tocarlo. Los rosales se utilizan principalmente en la producción de "
"tintes."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:209
msgid "Lilac"
msgstr "Lila"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:210
msgid ""
"A lilac is a large plant which occupies two blocks. It is mainly used in dye "
"production."
msgstr ""
"Una lila es una planta grande que ocupa dos bloques. Se utiliza "
"principalmente en la producción de tintes."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:225
msgid "Sunflower"
msgstr "Girasol"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:226
msgid ""
"A sunflower is a large plant which occupies two blocks. It is mainly used in "
"dye production."
msgstr ""
"Un girasol es una planta grande que ocupa dos bloques. Se utiliza "
"principalmente en la producción de tintes."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:269
msgid "Double Tallgrass"
msgstr "Doble hierba alta"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:270
msgid ""
"Double tallgrass a variant of tall grass and occupies two blocks. It can be "
"harvested for wheat seeds."
msgstr ""
"La doble hierba alta es una variante de hierba alta y ocupa dos bloques. Se "
"puede cosechar para obtener semillas de trigo."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:286
msgid "Large Fern"
msgstr "Helecho grande"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:287
msgid ""
"Large fern is a variant of fern and occupies two blocks. It can be harvested "
"for wheat seeds."
msgstr ""
"El helecho grande es una variante del helecho y ocupa dos bloques. Se puede "
"cosechar para obtener semillas de trigo."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:303
msgid "Tall Grass"
msgstr "Hierba alta"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:305
msgid ""
"Tall grass is a small plant which often occurs on the surface of grasslands. "
"It can be harvested for wheat seeds. By using bone meal, tall grass can be "
"turned into double tallgrass which is two blocks high."
msgstr ""
"La hierba alta es una planta pequeña que a menudo se encuentra en la "
"superficie de los pastizales. Se puede cosechar para semillas de trigo. "
"Mediante el uso de polvo de hueso, la hierba alta se puede convertir en "
"doble hierba alta que tiene dos bloques de altura."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:349
#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:372
msgid "Fern"
msgstr "Helecho"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:350
msgid ""
"Ferns are small plants which occur naturally in jungles and taigas. They can "
"be harvested for wheat seeds. By using bone meal, a fern can be turned into "
"a large fern which is two blocks high."
msgstr ""
"Los helechos son plantas pequeñas que se producen naturalmente en las selvas "
"y taigas. Se pueden cosechar para semillas de trigo. Al usar harina de "
"hueso, un helecho se puede convertir en un helecho grande que tiene dos "
"bloques de altura."

